{"tid":2371461,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"班主任屈我係危險人物之後揾人圍毆我，再迫我退學！","createTime":"2021-01-19T01:39:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T19:40:02.000Z","uid":380120,"like":3,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"2899927f9ba323d8c58488c98f6a5daacd33fc3e","tid":2371461,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T01:39:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uve5N6B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuve5N6B.jpg&h=7e4f7d34&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n我上學上左半年，過左多年荒島生活之後。<br />\n佢話「<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我私下問左其他同學，佢地都話你係危險人物，所以我要保護佢地，一定要整死你為止。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n我話「咩事，你誰，我在哪？」<br />\n佢話「你死緊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n我叫佢解釋「你誰？誰講甚麼，誰？你又想點！」<br />\n佢話「<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔話你知，淨係通知你聲，你死緊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n我話「你無證據，又唔清唔楚，憑咩屈我！」<br />\n佢話「吹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我會將你調到角落，再周圍空晒啲位，等你自閉柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你死緊」<br />\n之後佢就揾人唔知咩人，又揾人叫我退學。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da946bd674c68aa374811ba6e1ca522eca52120","tid":2371461,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T01:40:20.000Z","msg":"圍毆我"},{"pid":"08b1f804b8cd96b6be4ae22bab385871f27c1e04","tid":2371461,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T01:43:08.000Z","msg":"哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84eec8637807da62b4710288fbc9ba9d6fbd512b","tid":2371461,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T01:43:31.000Z","msg":"又停我課，又軟禁我，搞到我冇左成半個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲成個暑假驚冇書讀周圍揾band3學校求佢收我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />活在惶恐之中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5d6d6e8e4a406a823a05e842256356ad5c91e84","tid":2371461,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T01:47:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1dxCEiM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1dxCEiM.jpg&h=fa0a0511&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7adaa1119194112e70619c90c2ceb329603d1f7e","tid":2371461,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T01:49:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"245c98f5d0d2e2dcd53e95d107acbe0eacbb4da6","tid":2371461,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08b1f804b8cd96b6be4ae22bab385871f27c1e04","tid":2371461,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T01:43:08.000Z","msg":"哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T01:49:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3215f60082371c6b2e42f41bd57457d07ea0d77a","tid":2371461,"uid":105879,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T01:50:20.000Z","msg":"up乜鳩"},{"pid":"faca8658f31dca7bdd959cd8f0c0a41fc547ad8e","tid":2371461,"uid":33640,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T01:53:38.000Z","msg":"攬女鋸和牛，jar jar聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53c6d4214ef59785c989472acb021fec324dc83d","tid":2371461,"uid":237487,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T01:53:49.000Z","msg":"思覺失調？ 巴打睇下醫生好⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0810003877fec8553d9c10c7f95d932f6a81cb14","tid":2371461,"uid":381265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T01:54:15.000Z","msg":"樓主不如專心寫甜故"},{"pid":"343e988b1bc721e51ed7c1addf55367b18cdc4e1","tid":2371461,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"3215f60082371c6b2e42f41bd57457d07ea0d77a","tid":2371461,"uid":105879,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T01:50:20.000Z","msg":"up乜鳩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T01:56:22.000Z","msg":"我個班主任見我基層，過住荒島生活，所以調位果陣就話要特别隔開我，佢揾左個理由「<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我問左，因為其他同班唔知乜柒同學話你好恐怖，所以我有責任保護其他天真無邪弱小可憐嘅唔知乜柒學生。」<br />\n我問「佢乜水，佢講咩。」<br />\n佢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我應承要保護其他人私穩，費時你打鳩佢。佢先敢報串。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你up乜鳩。<br />\n之後我就走左。<br />\n點知佢之後真係隔離我仲揾人打我再迫我退學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a06f9e533f6f44bb92cc34e1947aad4b97a4d899","tid":2371461,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T01:58:28.000Z","msg":"好想識你"},{"pid":"6821db4e861c338d7b660d5844c92c390a01cfad","tid":2371461,"uid":317361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T02:00:47.000Z","msg":"精分現場"},{"pid":"588e1e86d23ff5f02376cd8f5e6e2feb709f0838","tid":2371461,"uid":51041,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T02:01:13.000Z","msg":"有病去睇醫生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37bbd6c3e76fd03184e7db1a81894c6b5b4607fd","tid":2371461,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T02:02:06.000Z","msg":"佢話「<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我主動問唔知乜柒，要唔知乜柒講你壞話，然後用來當證據，證明你係危險人物，我就可以做瓜你。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而你唔知佢乜柒又up乜柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知我揾左好多唔知乜柒講你壞話之後，你就係危險人物，我就會出招，你死緊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n我問「唔知乜柒究竟講左乜柒野。」<br />\n佢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我完全唔會同你講。封鎖你消息，然後再慢慢出招整死你。"},{"pid":"2d4aa67b836460cefe4fb39dc6010391a7772a8e","tid":2371461,"uid":1654,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T02:02:16.000Z","msg":"打字有得諗過度過先出文都寫到1999.<br />\n睇怕平時同人講野都係溝通唔到<br />\n然後發脾氣覺得其他人好蠢<br />\n最後比所有人杯葛"},{"pid":"102842b51dd0a9bbe889f5e87342951feb8207a4","tid":2371461,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"588e1e86d23ff5f02376cd8f5e6e2feb709f0838","tid":2371461,"uid":51041,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T02:01:13.000Z","msg":"有病去睇醫生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T02:02:28.000Z","msg":"我冇病<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31d740c1dbaf8b06996fd900abc83da29